-# file upon installation. If you did not use izpack, you must
-# find and replace all instances of (dollar)INSTALL_PATH and
-# (dollar)SYSTEM_java_io_tmpdir with appropriate values
-# (perhaps . and /var/tmp, respectively)
 #
